om/world/middle-east/missiles-drones-locked-on-us-targets-iran-warns-of-heavy-assault-after-tanker-strikes-in-gulf-of-oman/articleshow/130985047.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T06:19:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130985045,imgsize-1531995.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Pakistani national among 3 arrested in US for attempting to smuggle 89 firearms into Canada]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130985113.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Three men, including a Pakistani national, face serious charges in the US for attempting to smuggle 89 firearms, many reportedly stolen, into Canada.  Authorities apprehended the trio during a traffic stop, uncovering a significant cache of weapons.  The accused are now detained, facing lengthy prison sentences for their alleged involvement in illegal arms trafficking.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/faizan-ali-25pakistani-national-among-3-arrested-in-us-for-attempting-to-smuggle-89-firearms-into-canada/articleshow/130985113.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/faizan-ali-25pakistani-national-among-3-arrested-in-us-for-attempting-to-smuggle-89-firearms-into-canada/articleshow/130985113.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T06:38:30+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130985115,imgsize-528343.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Silicon Valley $162K, Dallas $113K: What's Trump's new plan to raise salary of H-1B workers]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982867.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/silicon-valley-162k-dallas-113k-whats-trumps-new-plan-to-raise-salary-of-h-1b-workers/articleshow/130982867.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/silicon-valley-162k-dallas-113k-whats-trumps-new-plan-to-raise-salary-of-h-1b-workers/articleshow/130982867.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T02:20:48+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130982884,imgsize-34540.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Former visa officer reveals 5 things interviewers notice apart from documents]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982648.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/former-visa-officer-reveals-5-things-interviewers-notice-apart-from-documents/articleshow/130982648.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/former-visa-officer-reveals-5-things-interviewers-notice-apart-from-documents/articleshow/130982648.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T01:07:15+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130982667,imgsize-96020.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Russia grateful to US for talks': Putin says Ukraine conflict ‘coming to an end’]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982369.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-grateful-to-us-for-talks-ukraine-conflict-coming-to-an-end-vladimir-putin-awaits-kyiv-response-on-pow-swap/articleshow/130982369.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-grateful-to-us-for-talks-ukraine-conflict-coming-to-an-end-vladimir-putin-awaits-kyiv-response-on-pow-swap/articleshow/130982369.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T00:17:05+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130982380,imgsize-16748.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Plane with 231 flyers runs over jaywalker, engine catches fire]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982606.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A Frontier Airlines flight bound for Los Angeles struck and killed a pedestrian who had jumped the airport's perimeter fence and was crossing the runway during takeoff. The incident sparked an engine fire, prompting the evacuation of 224 passengers and seven crew members. Minor injuries were reported among passengers, and authorities are investigating the fatal event.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/plane-with-231-flyers-runs-over-jaywalker-engine-catches-fire/articleshow/130982606.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/plane-with-231-flyers-runs-over-jaywalker-engine-catches-fire/articleshow/130982606.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T00:53:33+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130982622,imgsize-26410.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Keir Starmer appoints former Labour PM Gordon Brown as adviser after election flop]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982445.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Following significant local election losses, Labour leader Keir Starmer has appointed former Prime Minister Gordon Brown as a special envoy. This move comes amidst calls for Starmer's resignation from some party MPs, while voters express dissatisfaction with economic issues and immigration. Reform UK and the Greens have seen substantial gains in the polls.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/keir-starmer-appoints-gordon-brown-as-adviser-after-election-flop/articleshow/130982445.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/keir-starmer-appoints-gordon-brown-as-adviser-after-election-flop/articleshow/130982445.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T00:27:19+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Naomi Canton</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130982476,imgsize-38272.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Vatican softens towards LGBTQ+ Catholics]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982631.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Pope Leo XIV's Vatican is signaling a nuanced approach to LGBTQ+ Catholics, embracing dialogue while maintaining traditional stances on same-sex blessings. A recent Vatican report highlighted testimonies from gay Catholics, emphasizing social justice over sexual morality. This move has drawn praise from advocates and criticism from conservatives, underscoring the ongoing internal church debate.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vatican-softens-towards-lgbtq-catholics/articleshow/130982631.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vatican-softens-towards-lgbtq-catholics/articleshow/130982631.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T00:58:10+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130982647,imgsize-20604.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Three PIOs found guilty of Canada couple's murder]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982555.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Three Indian-origin men have been convicted of first-degree murder in Canada for the killing of Arnold and Joanne De Jong in Abbotsford in May 2022. The court found Gurkaran Singh, Abhijeet Singh, and Khushveer Toor played an integral role in the murders, which prosecutors stated were jointly planned for robbery.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/three-pios-found-guilty-of-canada-couples-murder/articleshow/130982555.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/three-pios-found-guilty-of-canada-couples-murder/articleshow/130982555.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T00:45:10+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130982562,imgsize-832070.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Hantavirus may've spread to remote island]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982652.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Health officials are working to contain a potential hantavirus spread after two new suspected cases emerged far from the cruise ship where the outbreak began. One case involves a passenger who fell ill after leaving the vessel, while another is a woman who sat near an infected individual on a plane.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/hantavirus-mayve-spread-to-remote-island/articleshow/130982652.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/hantavirus-mayve-spread-to-remote-island/articleshow/130982652.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T01:02:45+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130982684,imgsize-42800.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Israel widens Gaza control, plans more ops]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982547.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-widens-gaza-control-plans-more-ops/articleshow/130982547.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-widens-gaza-control-plans-more-ops/articleshow/130982547.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T00:42:26+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130982550,imgsize-81928.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US, Iran talks likely next week]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982526.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-iran-talks-likely-next-week/articleshow/130982526.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/us-iran-talks-likely-next-week/articleshow/130982526.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T00:38:56+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130982541,imgsize-2469052.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian-origin philanthropist Anil Kochhar pays off student loans for 176 graduates of North Carolina college: '80 years ago, my father...']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130982213.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-origin-philanthropist-anil-kochhar-pays-off-student-loans-for-176-graduates-of-north-carolina-80-years-ago-my-father-/articleshow/130982213.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us