son learning or continued remote education. This decision follows a nationwide safety assessment prompted by renewed regional tensions and emergency alerts. Authorities are prioritizing student and staff safety while ensuring educational continuity.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-to-decide-on-remote-or-in-person-classes-on-may-10-as-schools-and-universities-remain-on-alert/articleshow/130974232.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-to-decide-on-remote-or-in-person-classes-on-may-10-as-schools-and-universities-remain-on-alert/articleshow/130974232.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-09T14:16:36+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130974255,imgsize-78440.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who is Glenn Gibbins? Reform UK candidate who made racist remarks against Nigerians wins key England seat]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130980205.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/melt-them-down-and-fill-in-the-potholes-reform-uk-candidate-who-made-remarks-against-nigerians-wins-key-seat-in-england/articleshow/130980205.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/melt-them-down-and-fill-in-the-potholes-reform-uk-candidate-who-made-remarks-against-nigerians-wins-key-seat-in-england/articleshow/130980205.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-09T21:13:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130980209,imgsize-93390.cms"/></item></channel></rss>